description:
Join us on a journey through time, tracing the roots of our spiritual family and the story of how the Reformation unfolded over the centuries. We travel to Italy, France, Germany, Scotland, Switzerland, Czech Republic, Wales, and England - the homelands of forefathers such as John Wycliffe, Martin Luther, Columbanus, Aidan, and John Calvin.
